Sentencas: Electrocatalytic methane-to-syngas oxidation over metal-based electrodes in an SOFC reactor is discussed.
Titulo: Gas-phase electrocatalysis: methane oxidation to syngas in a solid oxide fuel cell reactor

Sentencas: The main attention is focused on the behavior of Pt and Ni electrodes, which demonstrate high electrocatalytic activity towards formation of syngas from methane.
Titulo: Gas-phase electrocatalysis: methane oxidation to syngas in a solid oxide fuel cell reactor
